{"tid":2170421,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"新盤動向：恆大 ‧ 珺瓏灣單日錄7宗成交　金額逾3578萬","createTime":"2020-08-23T09:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T09:20:56.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29592a279f56140b9c61eb15d733ab118f6bbca4","tid":2170421,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:08:31.000Z","msg":"屯門上車盤銷情理想。區內恆大 ‧ 珺瓏灣兩期於剛過去周六連錄7宗成交，當中包括6個2期單位，及1個位於1期單位，共涉金額逾3,578萬元。<br />\n當中2期5座22樓及21樓F單位，同屬開放式間隔，實用面積均為227方呎，分別以466.8萬及433.6萬元成交，呎價分別為20,564元及19,102元。而位於1期的2A座20樓D單位，實用面積為383方呎，屬兩房間隔，以692.8萬元沽出，呎價約18,089元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200823/mobile/bkn-20200823151325367-0823_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200823%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200823151325367-0823_00842_001.html&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTMjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=fe123fd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200823/mobile/bkn-20200823151325367-0823_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"be1490200606e72532983f6db90fc1c51a28fcea","tid":2170421,"uid":208376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"4千萬都無仲要係加埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7d26150a3af1354ab86c4ec624c9faf559d500","tid":2170421,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"第一輪買入轟龍灣係咩感覺"},{"pid":"1149ced458209d0b3a0f5e495335c498654820ec","tid":2170421,"uid":4258,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"2萬蚊呎買菌濃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}